2014-12-15
國立政治大學英文系將舉行系列讀書會,歡迎同學參加!!



 
政治大學英文系EARN (Enlightenment and Romanticism Network)研究團隊
謹訂於12月19日(五) 14:00-17:00於政治大學研究大樓250104室，進行系列讀書會。 
本次讀書會活動竭誠歡迎大家踴躍參與，相關訊息，敬請參閱如下 
 
Texts:  
1. Daniel S. Malachuk, "Emerson’s Politics, Retranscendentalized," A Political Companion to Ralph Waldo Emerson, ed. Alan M. Levine and Daniel S. Malachuk (UP of Kentucky, 2011), pp. 265-304. 
2. Michelle Kohler, "Scare Open My Eyes: Fleeting Visions and the Epistemology of Metaphor in Dickinson's Poetry," Miles of Stare: Transcendentalism and the Problem of Literary Vision in Nineteenth-Century America (U of Alabama P, 2014), pp. 105-36. 
Discussion Leaders: Drs John Michael Corrigan (柯瑞強) and Li-hsin Hsu (許立欣) 
 
